Brimelow, Peter. 1982b.  "Hands Off the Flat Tax: It Shouldn't Be
     Used for Raising the Take." <i>Barron's</i> (September 13).
<blockquote>
          Opposes using a flat-rate to increase overall taxation.
</blockquote><p>
Browning, Edgar K. 1976.  "The Marginal Cost of Public Funds."  <i>Journal of Political Economy</i>, vol. 84, no. 2 (April), pp. 283-298.
<blockquote>
                    The total welfare cost of the income tax in 1974 is
          estimated to be $19 billion and the marginal cost
          ranges from 9% to 16% of labor income.
</blockquote><p>
Browning, Edgar K. 1987.  "On the Marginal Welfare Cost of
     Taxation."  <i>American Economic Review</i>, vol. 77, no. 1
     (March), pp. 11-23.
